entry.title: Russia Claims Advances in Ukraine's South
entry.content: Moscow said its forces advanced in Ukraine’s southern Zaporizhzhia region as Kyiv’s Western allies continued pressuring Berlin to allow deliveries of German-made tanks to Ukraine.

entry.title: Eritrean Troops Endanger Ethiopian Peace Deal
entry.content: A peace accord meant to end Ethiopia’s civil war is hitting a stumbling block, as troops from neighboring Eritrea who had been fighting on the side of the federal government have failed to withdraw, local and international officials say.
